  "text": "For the microtubule disassembly assay, nocodazole (Sigma-Aldrich) was added directly to the growing medium at a 10 mM final concentration and cells were fixed in 2% paraformaldehyde (PFA) after 2 h. They were then stained according to the published protocols [CITATION_1] .",
